Package io.github.products

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Item
    Item will show that any implemented class can return the Id, Name, and Manufacturer of any instance of the class.
    MultimediaControl
    This interface forces any implemented class to have basic media controls.
    ScreenSpec
    Any class that can be described as a screen that has a resolution, refresh rate, and response time.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AudioPlayer
    A special product that has basic media controls.
    MoviePlayer  
    Product
    An abstract class that defines a product with an integer Id, and Strings name, manufacturer, and type.
    ProductionRecord
    Represents a recorded item that has been input into the system but has not yet been processed.
    Screen
    A screen that contains a resolution, refresh rate, and response time.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ItemType
    This contains the required constants that represent the available types for a product.
    MonitorType
    A list of constants describing the type of monitor on a movie player.
